%% CONDUIT: WSA calls each manager in a FIXED ORDER (1..4), feeding each returned DocDraft into the next call, then commits.
%% Managers are SIBLINGS of WSA. They never call each other. Order is carried by the 1..4 edge labels, not by manager-to-manager arrows.
